Class ReversedMobStoreScanner

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, ChangedReadersObserver, InternalScanner, KeyValueScanner, Shipper

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class ReversedMobStoreScanner
extends ReversedStoreScanner
    ReversedMobStoreScanner extends from ReversedStoreScanner, and is used to support reversed scanning in both the memstore and the MOB store.

        public boolean next(List<Cell> outResult,
                    ScannerContext ctx)
             throws IOException
        Firstly reads the cells from the HBase. If the cell is a reference cell (which has the reference tag), the scanner need seek this cell from the mob file, and use the cell found from the mob file as the result.
